text: James Horace Smith (October 20, 1852 - June 20, 1931) was the seventeenth Mayor of Orlando from 1904 to 1906. He died at the age of 78 in 1931 and was buried in Greenwood Cemeteryhttps://www.findagrave.com/memorial/14556037 ==References== Category:Mayors of Orlando, Florida Category:1852 births Category:1931 deaths
